---
title: Sesame Beef Tacos with Quick-Pickled Veggies & Sriracha Sour Cream
description: Instead of going the traditional route with these tacos, we decided to mix things up with a Korean-style sesame beef filling. The tacos get a tangy hit from pickled cucumber and radishes, and a kick from a sriracha-infused sour cream. The best part? Everything comes together in just 20 minutes from start to finish. Taco ’bout a weeknight win!
